{
  "stem": "10181.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Of course, they also performed for the inmates, you know, but the Germans had-- had them perform for them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And especially around Christmas time, you know, they could do that kind of thing, or any holiday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we, as I said, they tried to teach us to be good Jews in-- in the orphanage, and, of course, it was religious.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and-- and we had regular meal times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We had to pray before and after the meal, and, like I said, to try to have sort of classes within the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then we used to walk around the camp, look for friends and visit friends, and-- and it was confined.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was-- it was thousands upon thousands of people in a very small area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Difficult to-- it was maybe-- the whole camp might have been the size of a big football field, maybe a little bit bigger, but there were 20,000 or 30,000 people at the time there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, so that's how confined it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "You know, I mean, there was like a mass of people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And, of course, the-- the saddest thing was that every-- every-- nearly every week there was-- sometimes, there was a break.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "At one time, there was a break of a month or so, you know, for-- for whatever reason.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It was more technical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It wasn't that they didn't want to send the Jews away, there were other reasons for it, you know, within-- within the German system.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- what-- what was happening to the people once they left, we didn't know, because we were too far away.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
